<doc f='codebrowser/idlib/bv/Sphere.cpp' l='99'>/*
============
idSphere::RayIntersection

  Returns true if the ray intersects the sphere.
  The ray can intersect the sphere in both directions from the start point.
  If start is inside the sphere then scale1 &lt; 0 and scale2 &gt; 0.
============
*/</doc>
